The endpoints will look like so:

1. City and airport search using the Amadeus Airport & City Search API. This will allow your user to select their origin and destination.

2. Flight search using the Amadeus Flight Offers Search API. This will fetch a list of the cheapest flights between the origin and destination.

3. Confirm a flight using Amadeus Flight Offers Price API. This will confirm the validity of the fare with the airline before booking.

4. Flight booking using the Amadeus Flight Create Orders API. This will book the confirmed flight and generate a booking reference number.
